    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You fill the air with spinning daggers in a cube 5 feet on each side, centered on a point you choose within range. A creature takes [[/r 4d4]] slashing damage when it enters the spell's area for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 2d4]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
